704308f-b.title: Brooklyn: Flatbush Avenue - Hubbard Place
704308f-b.text:
(1)
1871 Flatbush Ave., east side, at Hubbard Place, showing the Simeon
Brown house. The house shown on the extreme right, is at the S.E. cor-
ners
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same, at a later date, and showing the Brown house prepara-
tory to removal to No. 17 Hubbard Place. Shown on the right, is a
new 2-story brick house, occupying the N.E. corner. Similar houses
were erected on the Brown site, and are designated as 1859-1869 Flat-
bush Ave.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
